<td align="center"><b>
<i>Megachile umatillensis</i> <font size="-1" face="sans-serif">&#40;Mitchell, 1927&#41;</font></b><br>
<small><i>Megachiloides umatillensis </i>Mitchell, 1927</small><p>
<a href="/mp/20q?search=Life">Life</a>
